{
  "stem": "4670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this one particular day, I was out, and this was in downtown Frankfurt, and they had these placards up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was on a kiosk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A kiosk is a circular kind of a structure where advertisements were put if someone wanted to rent an apartment or wanted to advertise selling a car or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were plastered with the stories about the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing that was so frightening were the photos were enlarged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were the photos that came right out that newspaper, right out of Der Stuermer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them were the ones that were babies were killed and the blood was being used for the Seder, our Passover service, and that the Jews drink that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They mix it into their wine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is something that, for a rational person, could not possibly believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was plastered all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was so offensive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the pictures of the Jews were people that I-- no one that I knew looked like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, horrible looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They looked like devils, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people were standing and they were laughing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the thing-- and I'm standing there and I'm thinking to myself, they're talking about me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's people like me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was very, extremely upsetting because [DRINKS] when you think about it, there are laws that protect animals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a dog, a bird had the protection of the government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were considered lepers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the terrible thing is if you stand aside and look, and you're not involved, it's different.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when you are the person that you are being ridiculed and laughed at, then you get a feeling that you're a non-person.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
